======
pdfgpt
======


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pdfgpt.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pdfgpt

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/pdfgpt/badge/?version=latest
